3. Ways of Performing Deeds
24. Unethical
At Sāvatthī.
“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element:
the faithless with the faithless …
shameless …
imprudent …
unethical …
witless …
The faithful with the faithful …
conscientious …
prudent...
ethical …
and the wise with the wise.”

